&lt;p&gt;    @afine &lt;br/&gt;
    No, I didn&apos;t run into this bug.&lt;br/&gt;
    I&apos;m renamed the JIRA, the pull request and the commit message.&lt;br/&gt;
    Thank you.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
